            <p>[---] بطل س</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
               <p>In the first edition of the relief the inscription was not mentioned, while a brief account is given on A. Łajtar's advice.</p>
                <p>For another similar relief with inscription of Hellenistic time, see <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr118600</ref>. Other ones exist, dating from the 
                Roman period.</p>
